'''Lopera''' is a city located in the [[Jaén (Spanish province)|province of Jaén]], Spain. According to the 2014 [[census]],<ref>[[Instituto Nacional de Estadística (Spain)|Instituto Nacional de Estadística (INE)]]</ref> the municipality has a population of 3,837 inhabitants.
